# Frontend Dockerfile

This is one of the most important files.

Our project uses a **multi-stage Docker build**.

Structure:

```dockerfile
FROM node:20-alpine AS build

WORKDIR /app

COPY package*.json .

RUN npm install

COPY .

RUN npm run build

FROM nginx:alpine

COPY --from=build ...

EXPOSE 80

CMD ...
```

